drm/cirrus: Fix cirrus drm driver for fbdev + qemu

Xorg fbdev driver requires smem_start/smem_len, otherwise
it tries to map 0 bytes as video memory.

Bugzilla: https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=856760
